data.title: CAHAYA 44 Inch Guitar Bag - Ultimate Protection with Style
data.body:
-

The CAHAYA 44 Inch Guitar Bag offers multi-pockets for convenient storage and organization. Specifically designed for jumbo and dreadnought guitars, it provides a snug fit and ample protection. With a vibrant yellow line design, this case stands out with style. Keep your guitar safe and secure on the go with this durable and stylish guitar bag from CAHAYA.
